============--- Fy_funtimes_remix---===============

In a nutshell, fy_funtimes_remix is a modified version of fy_funtimes
with a dim/spooky night setting.

Some features are:
- 3D skybox complete with moving clouds and buildings
- Modified terrain (Displacements)
- Thunder and rain

Please enjoy ^^
